# GopherSo API Tests

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/health

### Create User
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com", 
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get User (replace with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/users?id=USER_ID_HERE

### Create Post (replace with actual user ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello World",
  "content": "My first post on GopherSo!",
  "user_id": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "tags": ["hello", "first-post"]
}

### Get All Posts (Social Feed)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/posts

### Get Posts by User (replace with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/posts/by-user?user_id=USER_ID_HERE

### Get User with Posts (replace with actual user ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/users/posts?id=USER_ID_HERE